    rdfs:label """Possession …
Source: man previously arrested by AG Murrill's Louisiana Bureau of Investigation for more than 500 counts of
Possession of Child Sexual Abuse Material now facing 3 counts of First-Degree Rape
A man previously arrested by Attorney General Liz Murrill's Louisiana Bureau of Investigation agents back in
January of 2026 for 504 counts of Possession of Child Sexual Abuse Material is now facing three additional
counts of First-Degree Rape following the ongoing investigation""" ;
    cacontology-legal-outcomes:indictmentCounts 500 .

